README install wording now makes the release channels concrete for users:
- `main` = latest integrated install
- `VERSION=X.Y.Z` = pinned stable release
- `VERSION=X.Y.Z-rc.N` = pinned prerelease / RC

This makes the difference between main and stable tags explicit in the user-facing docs.
